<div class="line-top"></div><div class="styled-quote" style="padding: 1em 11em 1em 8em;">{{StructuredQuote|text=Silent stone of beige-green light,<br>Sparking softly through the night.<br>Bound as one, its currents flow,<br>Power born from its hidden glow.
